We fixed a few bugs and now the app is Apple Watch ready. No that doesn t mean you can watch films on your watch! But you can admire our selection and either start downloading or remind yourself to watch the film later . BUG FIXES AND UI TWEAKS Fixed a bug where download progress was lost if interrupted by moving to a mobile data connection Show watched state Improved payment screen layout on iPhone 6 Plus Footer text on film page is no longer unnecessarily truncated in certain languages Fixed crash when swiping star rating to far left Fixed low resolution icons on iPhone 6 Plus Merged newsletter options into standard list Added active state to subscription plan screen Improved reel selection presentation Removed unused Facebook sharing switch Fine tuned downloading notifications Show film immediately when following deep links i.e. don t go via the mosaic screen Show alert when deep link is not possible with link to film page on mubi.com Fixed broken pre login transitions when a user had logged in and out again Ensured film selection is always 100 accurate even in unexpected conditions Fixed crash when returning to mosaic screen if the viewed film had disappeared Fixed glitch when logging in with Facebook via Safari STATE RESTORATION If app is closed down in the background it will do a better job of returning the user to their previous context
Fixed some stability issues affecting certain users Some minor user interface tweaks New in 2.0 Improved responsive design Fixed some long standing stability issues
New responsive designs

Improved downloading experience Made several small user interface improvements Improved presentation in different languages Improved synchronisation of account settings between devices New sharing controls and addition of Pinterest sharing Fixed some issues that were causing crashing for some users Fixed the Error 8 problem that was affecting some users Added ability to send an error report for users experiencing problems

Improvements to downloading experience and stability Improved first run and on boarding experience Improved design for iPhone film view Don t prompt for Facebook credentials if they are already granted iPhone alerts may now be dismissed with tap Improvements for offline messaging Fix for occasionally broken synopsis text Fix for navigation buttons sometimes becoming disabled incorrectly Fix for a crash when going to subscription screen too quickly on startup Better price formatting iPhone layout fixes
iPhone support! Download system overhauled for improved performance and reliability Networking system overhauled Improved error messages Visual improvements Remembers viewing status more reliably
